  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983340/extras/b5666986f8a45719d4678131edc147aa.avif?t=1543484369\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>Hayate is stranded from the future to another era when brutal and full of intrigues pirates are dominant. He accidentally meets a beautiful woman pirate named Carmen who brings a secret map which leads to an immortal treasure. Hayate will face a sly pirate captain, a tough commander, a mysterious necromancer and a wondeful creature mermaid.<br><br>FEATURES :<br>- Exciting storyline in visual novel style<br>- 5 Waifu : Pirate, Pirate Captain, Commander, Necromancer and Mermaid<br>- Cool pirate music theme<br>- Match-3 with RPG elements<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983340/extras/83ce852da805994cd2937d88b55a923e.avif?t=1543484369\" width=480 height=316 /></span>",
